T02D3565:196a-1: a'arya shr'i ma t'i ku ru kulle s'a dha nam /
T02D3565:196a-3: dpal ldan 'phags ma rigs byed ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3565:196a-4: 'phags ma ku ru ku lle la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3565:196a-5: rang gi snying gar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la hr'i:yig
T02D3565:196a-6: las skyes pa'i autpa la dmar po'i dbus su hr'i:yig
T02D3565:196a-7: gis mnan pa bsams la de yongs su gyur pa
T02D3565:196a-8: las 'phags ma rigs byed ma sku mdog dmar mo
T02D3565:196a-9: padma dmar po dang zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs pa
T02D3565:196a-11: na bza' dmar po sna tshogs pa'i stong g-yogs can /
T02D3565:196a-12: 'od dpag tu med pas dbu brgyan pa /
T02D3565:196a-14: rtsa ba'i phyag dag gis autpa la dmar po'i mde
T02D3565:196a-15: 'us rnam par mdzes pa'i mda' dang bcas pa'i me
T02D3565:196a-16: tog gi gzhu rna ba'i rtsar 'gengs pa /
T02D3565:196a-17: g-yon sdong bu dang bcas pa'i autpa la dmar po kha bye ba bsnams pa /
T02D3565:196a-18: g-yas pa mtshog sbyin mdzad pa'o //
T02D3565:196a-19: sgeg pa'i nyams chen pos rol par bltas te /
T02D3565:196a-20: ye shes sems dpa' dang lhan cig tu byas nas
T02D3565:196a-21: rang gi lus kyi 'od zer dmar po'i lcags kyus
T02D3565:196a-29: bud med brgya stong la sogs pa'i tshogs shin tu
T02D3565:196b-0: gus par lus 'dud @196b cing mchog tu dbang du
T02D3565:196b-1: gyur par phyogs bcu rnams su yang dag par blta'o
T02D3565:196b-2: // aom ku ru kulle hr'i:sv'a h'a /
T02D3565:196b-3: zhes pa'i sngags bzlas pa 'bum nas brtsams nas /
T02D3565:196b-4: ji srid bcom ldan 'das ma mngon sum du ma gyur gyi bar du bzlas par bya'o //
T02D3565:196b-5: de nas 'ga' zhig dbang du bya par 'dod na
T02D3565:196b-6: ji ltar gsungs pa'i cho gas bzlas pa 'bum byas
T02D3565:196b-7: nas gus shing 'dud pa'i lha dang lha ma yin
T02D3565:196b-8: la sogs pa'i dbus su 'jug cing rang gi lus
T02D3565:196b-9: kyi 'od zer gyi lcags kyus bsgrub bya bkug la
T02D3565:196b-11: rang gi snying gar autpa la dmar po 'dab ma bcu drug pa /
T02D3565:196b-12: de'i snying gar yam bsams nas 'phags pa yan lag
T02D3565:196b-13: med pa'i rdo rjes gsungs pa'i rim pas bung ba'i
T02D3565:196b-15: de'i ming gi yi ge rang gi snying ga'i sngags
T02D3565:196b-16: kyis shin tu mnan nas de bzhin du mdas snying
T02D3565:196b-17: gar phug ste chags pa chen pos brgyal zhing gzhu
T02D3565:196b-18: rgyud kyis rkang pa bcings shing ske autpa la'i zhags
T02D3565:196b-19: pas bcings nas yang dag par bkug ste rang gi
T02D3565:196b-20: rkang pa dag gi drung du bsgyel la /
T02D3565:196b-21: skyes pa yin na lcags kyus snying gar dbug par bya'o //
T02D3565:196b-23: aom ku ru kulle che ge'am che ge mo a'a karsha ya hr'i:sv'a h'a /
T02D3565:196b-24: zhes bya ba'i sngags bzlas par bya'o //
T02D3565:196b-26: de la de bzhin du sngags la dbang du bya ba nang du spel la bzlas par bya'o //
T02D3565:196b-27: brgya bzlas pas skyes pa dang /
T02D3565:196b-30: blon po'i tshogs phal pa dbang du 'gyur ro //
T02D3565:196b-31: khri bzlas pas mnga' ris kyi 'jig rten no //
T02D3565:196b-33: 'bum phrag bdun gyis lha dang lha ma yin gyi bu mo'o //
T02D3565:196b-34: bye bas nam mkha' lding dang /
T02D3565:196b-35: glang po che sa srung gi bu la sogs pa'i lha'i dud 'gro rnams dang /
T02D3565:196b-36: dud 'gro phal pa rnams kyang ngo //
T02D3565:196b-37: gus pas rgyun mi chad par dus ring po dpag
T02D3565:196b-38: tu med par bzlas nas gsum yang dbang du byed
